description.en:
Goat Cash uses revolutionary Artificial Goat Intelligence (AGI) via it's dApp (distributed application) to enable the the Proof-of-Goat (PoG) algorithm. An advanced machine learning algorithm to deliver GOAT tokens to its shepherds. On top of this the Gestation (staking) of 30 days allows you to earn 1%/month on top of an associated dApp profits for the top 30 token holders.

Partnering with World Vision we will be delivering real goats to communities in need around the world. Check our roadmap and join us on this fabulous journey.
